data.description: Welcome to the wonderful Carrington community of Covington Park, where the concept of "home" goes beyond four walls and extends to a vibrant, welcoming neighborhood that offers multiple pools, splash pad, newly renovated fitness center, basketball  & tennis courts, dog park, nature trails and playgrounds. Its location is very ideal for its close proximity to I-75, walking distance to the elementary school, shopping and hospital. This home is situated on a CUL-DE-SAC which offers a sense of safety and further fosters that sense of community that is so desired.   Our home offers spacious living that flows seamlessly into one another, creating a harmonious atmosphere that promotes interaction and connection. The SPACIOUS KITCHEN provides the ideal backdrop for gatherings, allowing you to entertain all who matter most to you! With open-concept living and an OVERSIZED BACKYARD, this property is more than a home; it's a destination for all the cherished moments of life. Come be a part of this warm and welcoming community, and create a future filled with endless possibilities. AC 2017, UV light added to HVAC 2021, Water Heater 2019, Appliances 2021, new LVP flooring and carpet. Welcome home.
